OL,3,CRhigos Mountain Road to close for more
OL,4,Cthan three months for repairs
OL,6,FA Valleys road will close for more
OL,7,Fthan three months to replace rock
OL,8,Fnetting that was destroyed in a
OL,9,Fwildfire.
OL,11,FThe A4061 Rhigos Mountain Road, which
OL,12,Fconnects people living in both the
OL,13,FRhondda and Cynon Valley, will shut
OL,14,Ffrom July 22 to the end of October so
OL,15,Fthe repair work can take place.
OL,17,FBack in August 2022, a grass fire
OL,18,Fmelted fencing on the roadside
OL,19,Fallowing boulders to fall onto the
OL,20,Froad itself.
