OL,3,CRhigos Mountain Road to close for more
OL,4,Cthan three months for repairs
OL,6,FPeople were warned to stay away from
OL,7,Fthe area and specialist rope access
OL,8,Fcontractors were brought in to remove
OL,9,Floose material. They also inspected
OL,10,Fthe netting to assess the full scale
OL,11,Fof damage, with emergency works
OL,12,Fcarried out to make the area safe.
OL,14,FThe council said at the time that the
OL,15,Froute was "extremely dangerous" with
OL,16,Frocks falling on to the road and urged
OL,17,Fpeople not to attempt to access it.
OL,19,FRhondda Cynon Taff Council has since
OL,20,Fannounced a major repair scheme to
OL,21,Frectify the damage.
