OL,6,FThe work will be carried out at the
OL,7,Fsouthern end of the A4061 Rhigos
OL,8,FMountain Road, over a length of
OL,9,Fapproximately 375-metres.
OL,11,FThe council said the public right of
OL,12,Fway beneath A4061 Rhigos Mountain Road
OL,13,Fwill "remain open for experienced
OL,14,Fwalkers, but this route is not
OL,15,Fsuitable for cyclists."
