OL,6,FRhondda Cynon Taf Council's Director
OL,7,Fof Highways, Streetcare and
OL,8,FTransportation Services, said: "While
OL,9,Fthere will be disruption due to this
OL,10,Fscheme, planned works seek to minimise
OL,11,Fthis and reduce the risk of sporadic
OL,12,Fand longer term closures.
OL,14,F"These complex engineering works are
OL,15,Fnecessary to ensure the safety of this
OL,16,Fimportant route, respond to the damage
OL,17,Fcaused by grassfires in 2022, and
OL,18,Fimportantly seek to future-proof the
OL,19,Fwider structural integrity of this
OL,20,Fmountain route.
