OL,6,F"The works are unable to be carried
OL,7,Fout either wholly or partially at
OL,8,Fnight, due to the complex nature of
OL,9,Fthe remediation of the rock slope.
OL,10,FDaylight hours are essential to
OL,11,Fprovide safe conditions for the
OL,12,Fworkforce to operate heavy machinery
OL,13,Fand undertake rope access to the large
OL,14,Frockface and rock netting.
OL,16,F"The start of the works have been
OL,17,Fscheduled for the school summer
OL,18,Fholiday to minimise disruption as much
OL,19,Fas possible.
