OL,3,CRhigos Mountain Road to close for more
OL,4,Cthan three months for repairs
OL,6,F"The Council recognises the
OL,7,Fsignificant inconvenience this closure
OL,8,Fwill cause for residents of both the
OL,9,FRhondda and Cynon Valleys, but due to
OL,10,Fthe complicated civil engineering that
OL,11,Fis needed, there are no other viable
OL,12,Falternatives available to complete
OL,13,Fthese very necessary works."
OL,15,FThe council added that although work
OL,16,Fis scheduled to be completed by the
OL,17,Fend of October, the official road
OL,18,Fclosure notice goes into December to
OL,19,Fallow the council to keep it shut for
OL,20,Flonger in case of any delays.
